Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 4.14 18/59] video: fbdev: kyro: Error out if 'pixclock' equals zero
Date:   Thu,  9 Sep 2021 07:58:19 -0400
Message-Id: <20210909115900.149795-18-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.30.2
